description: Braza Grill has been providing Utah’s Brazilian barbecue fix for over 12 years with their two bustling brick & mortar locations in Murray in Lehi. Now the streets of Salt Lake City will also get a taste of this delicious authentic cuisine, all thanks to Braza Express!Tender cuts of choice grilled meats, tasty sides, and fresh salads, are a few of the tasty items you’ll find on this mobile menu. With brilliant quality of flavor and service, if you’re craving the best, be sure to try Braza Express!
name: Braza Express
